# A concise description of what this element means (e.g. for use in autogenerated summaries).
#: StructureDefinition.element.CareTeam.identifier/short
msgid "Identifiant du cercle de soins"
msgstr "Identifiant du cercle de soins"

# This element is for traceability of why the element was created and why the constraints exist as they do. This may be used to point to source materials or specifications that drove the structure of this element.
#: StructureDefinition.element.CareTeam.identifier.value/requirements
msgid "This version of the profile requires an ID identifying this profile as an IHE PCC Dynamic Care Team"
msgstr "This version of the profile requires an ID identifying this profile as an IHE PCC Dynamic Care Team"

# A concise description of what this element means (e.g. for use in autogenerated summaries).
#: StructureDefinition.element.CareTeam.status/short
msgid "Statut du cercle de soins.
 valeurs autorisées : proposed | active | suspended | inactive | entered-in-error"
msgstr "Statut du cercle de soins.
 valeurs autorisées : proposed | active | suspended | inactive | entered-in-error"

# A concise description of what this element means (e.g. for use in autogenerated summaries).
#: StructureDefinition.element.CareTeam.category/short
msgid "Type d’équipe. Une personne prise en charge ne peut avoir qu’un cercle de soins donc cet élément n’est pas utilisé."
msgstr "Type d’équipe. Une personne prise en charge ne peut avoir qu’un cercle de soins donc cet élément n’est pas utilisé."

# A concise description of what this element means (e.g. for use in autogenerated summaries).
#: StructureDefinition.element.CareTeam.name/short
msgid "Nom de l’équipe tel que « Cercle de soins de Mr Dupont »."
msgstr "Nom de l’équipe tel que « Cercle de soins de Mr Dupont »."

# A concise description of what this element means (e.g. for use in autogenerated summaries).
#: StructureDefinition.element.CareTeam.subject/short
msgid "Le sujet du cercle de soins est une personne prise en charge (« Patient »)."
msgstr "Le sujet du cercle de soins est une personne prise en charge (« Patient »)."

# A concise description of what this element means (e.g. for use in autogenerated summaries).
#: StructureDefinition.element.CareTeam.encounter/short
msgid "La rencontre au cours de laquelle le cercle de soins a été créé ou à laquelle la création de cet enregistrement est étroitement associée n’est pas utilisée dans ce volet."
msgstr "La rencontre au cours de laquelle le cercle de soins a été créé ou à laquelle la création de cet enregistrement est étroitement associée n’est pas utilisée dans ce volet."

# Explanatory notes and implementation guidance about the data element, including notes about how to use the data properly, exceptions to proper use, etc. (Note: The text you are reading is specified in ElementDefinition.comment).
#: StructureDefinition.element.CareTeam.encounter/comment
msgid "This profile allows for CareTeam creation outside of the context of an encounter or episode."
msgstr "This profile allows for CareTeam creation outside of the context of an encounter or episode."

# A concise description of what this element means (e.g. for use in autogenerated summaries).
#: StructureDefinition.element.CareTeam.period/short
msgid "Période couverte par le cercle de soins."
msgstr "Période couverte par le cercle de soins."

# This element is for traceability of why the element was created and why the constraints exist as they do. This may be used to point to source materials or specifications that drove the structure of this element.
#: StructureDefinition.element.CareTeam.period/requirements
msgid "Allows tracking what team(s) are in effect at a particular time. This version of the profile requires period for the CareTeam."
msgstr "Allows tracking what team(s) are in effect at a particular time. This version of the profile requires period for the CareTeam."

# A concise description of what this element means (e.g. for use in autogenerated summaries).
#: StructureDefinition.element.CareTeam.period.start/short
msgid "Date de création du cercle de soins."
msgstr "Date de création du cercle de soins."

# Explanatory notes and implementation guidance about the data element, including notes about how to use the data properly, exceptions to proper use, etc. (Note: The text you are reading is specified in ElementDefinition.comment).
#: StructureDefinition.element.CareTeam.period.start/comment
msgid "This version of the profile requires at least a start time for the CareTeam."
msgstr "This version of the profile requires at least a start time for the CareTeam."

# A concise description of what this element means (e.g. for use in autogenerated summaries).
#: StructureDefinition.element.CareTeam.period.end/short
msgid "Date de fin d'existence du cercle de soins."
msgstr "Date de fin d'existence du cercle de soins."

# A concise description of what this element means (e.g. for use in autogenerated summaries).
#: StructureDefinition.element.CareTeam.participant/short
msgid "Membres du cercle de soins."
msgstr "Membres du cercle de soins."

# Explanatory notes and implementation guidance about the data element, including notes about how to use the data properly, exceptions to proper use, etc. (Note: The text you are reading is specified in ElementDefinition.comment).
#: StructureDefinition.element.CareTeam.participant/comment
msgid "It is possible for a care team to be set up with roles specified only, before actual participants are invited into or identified as team members"
msgstr "It is possible for a care team to be set up with roles specified only, before actual participants are invited into or identified as team members"

# A concise description of what this element means (e.g. for use in autogenerated summaries).
#: StructureDefinition.element.CareTeam.participant.member/short
msgid "Il s’agit d’une personne (Professionnel ou Personne Tierce) ou d’une Entité qui fait partie du Cercle de Soins d’un Usager"
msgstr "Il s’agit d’une personne (Professionnel ou Personne Tierce) ou d’une Entité qui fait partie du Cercle de Soins d’un Usager"

# This element is for traceability of why the element was created and why the constraints exist as they do. This may be used to point to source materials or specifications that drove the structure of this element.
#: StructureDefinition.element.CareTeam.participant.member/requirements
msgid "Need to know who the member is if participant is required.
This version of the profile requires that a DynamicCareTeam be referenced when the member is a care team."
msgstr "Need to know who the member is if participant is required.
This version of the profile requires that a DynamicCareTeam be referenced when the member is a care team."

# Explanatory notes and implementation guidance about the data element, including notes about how to use the data properly, exceptions to proper use, etc. (Note: The text you are reading is specified in ElementDefinition.comment).
#: StructureDefinition.element.CareTeam.participant.period/comment
msgid "Chaque membre du Cercle de Soins dispose d’une date de début et une date de fin (optionnelle) de participation à ce cercle."
msgstr "Chaque membre du Cercle de Soins dispose d’une date de début et une date de fin (optionnelle) de participation à ce cercle."

# A concise description of what this element means (e.g. for use in autogenerated summaries).
#: StructureDefinition.element.CareTeam.participant.period.start/short
msgid "Date de début de participation au cercle de soin de la personne prise en charge Un membre doit pouvoir entrer et sortir plusieurs fois du cercle de soins. Pour satisfaire cette demande, il est possible de créer plusieurs instances de l’élément participant faisant référence au même membre mais à des périodes différentes."
msgstr "Date de début de participation au cercle de soin de la personne prise en charge Un membre doit pouvoir entrer et sortir plusieurs fois du cercle de soins. Pour satisfaire cette demande, il est possible de créer plusieurs instances de l’élément participant faisant référence au même membre mais à des périodes différentes."

# A concise description of what this element means (e.g. for use in autogenerated summaries).
#: StructureDefinition.element.CareTeam.managingOrganization/short
msgid "L’organisation responsable du cercle de soins."
msgstr "L’organisation responsable du cercle de soins."

# A concise description of what this element means (e.g. for use in autogenerated summaries).
#: StructureDefinition.element.CareTeam.telecom/short
msgid "Point de contact central du cercle de soins (qui s’applique à tous les membres) ; élément non utilisé dans le cadre de ce volet."
msgstr "Point de contact central du cercle de soins (qui s’applique à tous les membres) ; élément non utilisé dans le cadre de ce volet."

# A concise description of what this element means (e.g. for use in autogenerated summaries).
#: StructureDefinition.element.CareTeam.note/short
msgid "Commentaires sur le cercle de soins."
msgstr "Commentaires sur le cercle de soins."

